high_descs: Turn right, move to the sink.
Pick up the soap, right of the sink.
Bring the soap to the left side of the sink.
Wash the soap in the sink with water.
Bring the washed soap to the cabinet left of the sink.
Put the soap in the the lower cabinet, left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed soap in the cabinet left of the sink.

high_descs: Take a step forward then turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the bar of pink soap that's in front of you.
Take two steps to your left then turn right.
Get the soap wet in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Open the cabinet under the drawer to the left of the sink and put the soap down there before closing the door again..
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the sink.
Pick the bar of soap up from the counter to the right side of the sink.
Move the the left and turn to face the left side of the sink.
Put the soap in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the soap back up.
Back up and face the tall white cabinet to the left of the sink.
Open the lower cabinet and put the soap inside and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap in a cabinet.
